---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";

const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer
  class="bg-[#0c0a09] border-t border-[#C8AA6E]/30 py-16 relative overflow-hidden"
>
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom,rgba(200,170,110,0.15),transparent_70%)]"
  >
  </div>

  <div
    class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-[#C8AA6E]/20"
  >
    <Icon
      name="mdi:pentagram"
      class="w-64 h-64 animate-spin-slow duration-[120s]"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <h2
      class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-cinzel text-[#e7e5e4] mb-6 drop-shadow-lg"
    >
      ¿Buscas una Alianza?
    </h2>

    <p
      class="text-[#a8a29e] font-serif italic text-lg mb-10 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed"
    >
      "Mi espada (teclado) y mis hechizos (código) están listos para tu próxima
      campaña. ¿Unimos fuerzas para conquistar el reino digital?"
    </p>

    <a
      href="mailto:miguel.emezero@gmail.com"
      class="group relative inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-10 py-4 bg-[#1c1917] border border-[#C8AA6E] text-[#C8AA6E] font-cinzel font-bold tracking-widest hover:bg-[#C8AA6E] hover:text-[#0c0a09] transition-all duration-300 mb-16 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(200,170,110,0.1)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(200,170,110,0.4)]"
    >
      <Icon
        name="mdi:feather"
        class="w-6 h-6 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform"
      />
      ENVIAR UN CUERVO
    </a>

    <div class="flex justify-center gap-12 mb-12">
      <a
        href="https://linkedin.com/in/bymiguelmartinez"
        target="_blank"
        class="group flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-[#78716c] hover:text-[#C8AA6E] transition-colors"
      >
        <div
          class="p-3 border border-[#44403c] rounded-full group-hover:border-[#C8AA6E] transition-colors bg-[#0c0a09]"
        >
          <Icon name="mdi:linkedin" class="w-6 h-6" />
        </div>
        <span
          class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 transform -translate-y-2 group-hover:translate-y-0"
          >Alliance</span
        >
      </a>

      <a
        href="https://github.com/miguel0exe"
        target="_blank"
        class="group flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-[#78716c] hover:text-[#C8AA6E] transition-colors"
      >
        <div
          class="p-3 border border-[#44403c] rounded-full group-hover:border-[#C8AA6E] transition-colors bg-[#0c0a09]"
        >
          <Icon name="mdi:github" class="w-6 h-6" />
        </div>
        <span
          class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 transform -translate-y-2 group-hover:translate-y-0"
          >Grimoires</span
        >
      </a>
    </div>

    <div
      class="border-t border-[#44403c] pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center text-xs text-[#57534e] font-mono gap-4"
    >
      <p>© {currentYear} Miguel Ángel. Inscribed in the Digital Stone.</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span>Built with</span>
        <Icon
          name="simple-icons:astro"
          class="w-4 h-4 hover:text-[#C8AA6E] transition-colors"
        />
        <span>&</span>
        <Icon
          name="simple-icons:tailwindcss"
          class="w-4 h-4 hover:text-cyan-500 transition-colors"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
